        "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
        "body": "It appears that inputting the password only serves to clear the overlay, which one could still do from the Javascript Console and access all of the features available on the page. Therefore, we also need to restrict the Firebase database calls based on the authentication. That's difficult to do when everything is on the same page. I recommend moving the sign in process to a separate page, using either the official pennkey login, or [Firebase Auth](https://firebase.google.com/docs/auth/) so that we may use token-based authentication. That way, we can restrict access to the TA page and all of it's functionality."
    },
